{"tid":1875010,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"2月12號法庭聲援（懇請大家抽空出席）","createTime":"2020-02-11T13:46:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-12T02:48:59.000Z","uid":292499,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5988f11dd70caedfa2389e4ea0d7ab0f0acd7e8a","tid":1875010,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T13:46:01.000Z","msg":"【#上庭聲援 - 2 月 1 2 日 星期三】<br />\n<br />\n🏛高 等 法 院 3 樓 1 庭<br />\n👩🏻&zwj;⚖️杜麗冰法官<br />\n► 10:30 am<br />\n👤鄺(20)🛑<strong>已還押85天</strong> 申請保釋（#1118理大 暴動）<br />\n► 11:30 am<br />\n👤梁(26)🛑<strong>已還押228天</strong> 申請保釋（#0616中環 誤殺:涉推跌六旬漢兩日後死亡 #非反送案件）"},{"pid":"b47389417416d7c46bea558a7cd034fea74e39af","tid":1875010,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T13:46:18.000Z","msg":"#聲援注意 #旁聽須知 #遮陣接送<br />\n⚠️⚠️⚠️⚠️⚠️⚠️⚠️⚠️⚠️<br />\n以下為法庭旁聽須知要點，十分重要，請大家旁聽前睇睇，唔好留壞印象比法官。<br />\n<br />\n1⃣👨&zwj;👩&zwj;👧&zwj;👦旁聽須知<br />\n➖請預早開庭前15-30分鐘到所屬樓層排隊取籌🔖<br />\n➖法院大樓不能拍照 / 攝影📷<br />\n➖法庭範圍內保持安靜，切勿喧嘩🗣勿嗌口號<br />\n➖手機請轉為靜音/關機，亦部份法官不容許法庭內使用手機<br />\n➖遲到/已開庭，庭內未滿亦可進入，進出請向法官鞠躬<br />\n➖庭內不能戴帽，入庭前請除帽<br />\n➖部份法官不容許戴口罩<br />\n➖庭內不準飲食<br />\n➖主要以英語進行審訊，不清楚可以睇我哋嘅文字直播台 @youarenotalonehk_live<br />\n➖高等法院大樓1樓至14樓，需在地下進行安檢；低層4樓法庭的人士，則需在低層4樓進行安檢；低層3樓至地下，並不需要接受保安檢查<br />\n<br />\n法院禮儀請參閱：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcfa.hk/tc/visiting/attending/other/etiquette/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcfa.hk%2Ftc%2Fvisiting%2Fattending%2Fother%2Fetiquette%2Findex.html&d=k4A9UPuxEtmwSexvyTVA%2BXpsBjqOi2zFRj9KJcX5ApM%3D&h=c1c861ae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcfa.hk/tc/visiting/attending/other/etiquette/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n2⃣💝貼心提示：<br />\n拘捕後直接過堂嘅手足，袋可能被狗仔咬爛咗，大家見到不妨遞個有色膠袋或者環保袋比佢哋啦<br />\n<br />\n3⃣☔️遮陣接送<br />\n保釋處理：將由正門離開，保釋手續需時，請耐心等候，可幫手足call定的士， 遮陣接送手足亦可先向家屬溝通， 避免誤會<br />\n<br />\n4⃣🚓還押送車<br />\n還押處理手足，將由側門 / 停車場離開，可等懲教車送車<br />\nP.S. 懲教不是POPO唔好屌佢哋"},{"pid":"3d2787c246ffbbd4b22d347593300ccf2fba700c","tid":1875010,"uid":89006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T13:46:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"525aedc4aff1e7ff6787ceb1bb986d3f4168975c","tid":1875010,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T13:46:28.000Z","msg":"詳情可follow被捕人士關注組<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk&d=k4A9UPuxEtmwSexvyTVA%2BXpsBjqOi2zFRj9KJcX5ApM%3D&h=3d2c87e1\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk</a><br />\n<br />\nIG <br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/youarenotalonehk?igshid=knzk6gr75kea\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fyouarenotalonehk%3Figshid%3Dknzk6gr75kea&d=k4A9UPuxEtmwSexvyTVA%2BXpsBjqOi2zFRj9KJcX5ApM%3D&h=4c584c8f\" target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/youarenotalonehk?igshid=knzk6gr75kea</a>"},{"pid":"3320ac6facfb06a7cd4e73cddb430bc05d2e2b16","tid":1875010,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T13:46:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YvkbZiy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYvkbZiy.jpg&h=7a636f66&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"93757a88844db867ae8a6e5b1168502c3c4c0c39","tid":1875010,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T13:47:16.000Z","msg":"#上庭聲援 #交通資訊 <br />\n📍高等法院交通<br />\n各條路線及落車地點如下：<br />\n<br />\n<strong>新界</strong><br />\n北區：978 [政府總部]<br />\n大埔區：307 [海富中心]<br />\n馬鞍山：681 [高等法院]<br />\n沙田：88R, 182 [高等法院]<br />\n屯門：960, 961, 962B, 962X [力寶中心]<br />\n天水圍：967 [金鐘(西)總站]，969 [力寶中心]<br />\n元朗：968 [力寶中心]<br />\n荃灣：930 [金鐘站]， 934 [力寶中心]⚠️服務時間至13:00、936 [政府總部]⚠️服務時間至12:00<br />\n葵涌：930 [金鐘站]<br />\n青衣：948 [力寶中心]<br />\n<br />\n<strong>九龍：</strong><br />\n藍田：601  [海富中心]<br />\n觀塘區：101  [太古廣場]<br />\n黃大仙區：113 [太古廣場]<br />\n九龍城區：101 [太古廣場]、 111 [高等法院]<br />\n油尖旺區：104 [太古廣場]、905 [政府總部]<br />\n大角咀：914 [力寶中心]<br />\n深水埗區：905 [政府總部]、914 [力寶中心]<br />\n紅隧：101, 104, 113 [太古廣場]、 111, 109 [高等法院]<br />\n<br />\n<strong>港島：</strong><br />\n銅鑼灣：5X, 11 [金鐘站]<br />\n炮台山：25 [金鐘站]<br />\n香港仔：37A [太古廣場]<br />\n跑馬地：1, 5B [太古廣場]<br />\n嘉亨灣：2  [海富中心]<br />\n柴灣：780 [海富中心]<br />\n耀東邨：722  [海富中心]<br />\n鴨脷洲邨：90 [太古廣場]<br />\n利東邨：97 [太古廣場]<br />\n<br />\n<strong>交通資訊由【抗爭行動交通頻道】提供</strong>"},{"pid":"5e3d038a4e111683e86d5c854e495428d6264a1a","tid":1875010,"uid":66546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T13:47:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0d86ed07a2219d225eba7d1c02e9df64fd00600","tid":1875010,"uid":237300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T14:02:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31ad7f696d260fe8001fefb543358d9a76ffd676","tid":1875010,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T23:36:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">🛑突發聲援🛑 #新案件未知詳情 <br />\n<br />\n09:30 am - 觀 塘 裁 判 法 院<br />\n</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"0c3cbdfd78daa9cbc5f60057a55b7e8e605e9e7e","tid":1875010,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T23:36:50.000Z","msg":"觀塘要人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bae15c5d96a4f553ea0b322f9918d27e0fde0fe","tid":1875010,"uid":126305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T02:41:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fd1fa8f6ef52bd84627f5868b11c7b609ecf786e","tid":1875010,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T02:45:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19795a6c99068af323ed59a508e9cc0f9bccaad8","tid":1875010,"uid":269372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T02:45:52.000Z","msg":"